our name voted upon by all officers in the guild. If you receive a majority vote, you will be invited into the guild. Depending on your level, you will be either a Junior Member (below level 35) or a Senior Member (level 35 and above).<br><br>It is advised to post your interest in joining GC in this forum; especially if you do not have a sponsor yet. Please include your characters name, class, and level. One of our Membership Officers will attempt to contact you in game, or you can send a /tell to any officer that is online when you are. Please see the roster for a list of current officers.<br><br>*NOTE: I will be editing this document to include links for the roster and charter once they are completed.* <p><center><img src=http://www.griffinclaw.com/bios/oogbooger/oogie3.jpg></center></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/uoogbooger.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Oogbooger</A> at: 6/9/01 5:26:01 pm<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub12.ezboard.com/fgriffinclawwantingtojoingriffinclaw.showPrevMessage?topicID=51.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fgriffinclawwantingtojoingriffinclaw.emailToFriend?topicID=51.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fgriffinclawwantingtojoingriffinclaw.threadControl?topicID=51.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fgriffinclawwantingtojoingriffinclaw.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=51.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fgriffinclawwantingtojoin